B.X3=new A.bx("Rainmeter skins are published on DeviantArt.com under the \u201cOffBalance Creative Team\u201d alias. DeviantArt is a platform specialized in art projects of all forms, handmade or digital. It is a big market that creators can share or sell their creations, free or with a fee. This website has always been the home of the Rainmeter\u2019s skins and it\u2019s the main (if not the only) place where users can find these creations.\n\n\u201cOffBalance\u201d came to life after my personal experience on creating my own Rainmeter skins. These skins despite being created by one person are always inspired by other ones, either by their style or their features. As Rainmeter is open source, along with every skin created, each creator can borrow parts of code from everyone to create their own unique things. Just like that, I see my skins as a collective work, influenced by many other creators and by creating this alias, I want to include everyone that unknowingly took part of my creations. Its  tribute to every creator who either lent me their code or helped me with extensions and packages.",null,B.TZ,null,null,null,null)
